Incremental(递增的) Diff(差异)
Sublime Text includes a built-in diff(差异) functionality(功能) that tracks(追踪) changes to files being edited. The diff(差异) calculation(推算) is incremental(递增的), tracking(追踪) each buffer(缓冲) modification(修改) as it is performed(执行). It does not require(需要) the file be stored(存储) in a version control system, such as Git.

The exact(准确的) location(地址) of each addition(添加), modification(修改) and deletion(删除) is tracked(追踪). This is used to display markers(标记) in the gutter(排水沟), allow navigation(导航) between each change, display inline(内联的) diffs(差异) and allow for reverting(恢复) changes.

Diffs(差异) are calculated(推算) against the version of the file on disk, but Git repositories(存储库) can be configured(配置) to diff(差异) against HEAD, and the API allows files to be diffed(差异) against any content(内容).



